item.title: CVE-2023-41846|2024-09-26T14:12:24.575Z -- siemens -- tecnomatix%20plant%20simulation%20v2201
item.description: A vulnerability has been identified in Tecnomatix Plant Simulation V2201 (All versions < V2201.0008), Tecnomatix Plant Simulation V2302 (All versions < V2302.0002). The affected application is vulnerable to memory corruption while parsing specially crafted SPP files. This could allow an attacker to execute code in the context of the current process.
